<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5900592542309084919">William Raymond Manchester was an American author and biographer, notable as the bestselling author of 18 books that have been translated into 20 languages.He was awarded the National Humanities Medal and the Abraham Lincoln Literary Award.</span>

